Once you and Willie decided
to kick me to the curb,

42:47.524 --> 42:50.235
that was a motivating factor.

42:52.153 --> 42:54.614
So I thank you.

42:54.781 --> 42:57.534
If you hadn't been
so expedient with my ass,

42:57.659 --> 42:59.744
I may have never had
the stones to think about

42:59.911 --> 43:02.205
nothing but myself.

43:05.125 --> 43:08.086
I was gonna bring you up
when I made it.

43:08.253 --> 43:11.423
I had to get launched first.
That's just business.

43:11.589 --> 43:15.427
That had nothing to do
with our friendship.

43:15.593 --> 43:16.553
[Wild Bill] Mm-hmm.

43:17.971 --> 43:20.265
Mm-hmm.

43:20.432 --> 43:22.267
Wrote my accountant's
number on there.

43:23.977 --> 43:26.730
Next time, just call him.

43:30.817 --> 43:33.111
-Thank you.
-[Wild Bill sighs]

43:35.155 --> 43:38.158
Hey, uh, uh, Bill.

43:38.325 --> 43:41.453
[sighs]

43:41.619 --> 43:44.873
About the money.
Listen, uh...

43:45.040 --> 43:47.959
don't, uh...
don't tell Carol.

43:48.126 --> 43:51.463
Please.
Or my boys.

43:51.629 --> 43:52.839
It...

43:53.006 --> 43:54.632
it's embarrassing.

44:00.889 --> 44:03.224
You're a fucking genius, Tom.

44:03.391 --> 44:06.811
I mean it.
You are.

44:06.978 --> 44:10.440
I thought you'd protect me
from being a clown.

44:12.150 --> 44:14.527
Thought I'd spend my whole
life playing your shit.

44:16.404 --> 44:19.407
Instead I'm doing
"Heaven Forbidden."

44:22.160 --> 44:23.286
Godspeed, brother.

44:33.505 --> 44:36.341
[bluesy music plays]

44:36.466 --> 44:39.386
♪ ♪

44:39.511 --> 44:41.513
Hey, honey.
I, uh, sorry.

44:41.679 --> 44:43.431
Sorry to call so late.

44:43.556 --> 44:47.602
I went out with a couple
guys from the autograph expo.

44:47.769 --> 44:50.647
But good news--
they- they want to invest.

44:50.772 --> 44:54.192
So we're good for a while.

44:54.359 --> 44:55.693
So this was

44:55.860 --> 44:58.113
a successful trip.

44:58.279 --> 44:59.948
Ha.

45:00.115 --> 45:02.450
Uh, well,
I'll see you tomorrow.

45:04.452 --> 45:05.703
I love you.

45:07.247 --> 45:08.540
Bye.

45:21.553 --> 45:25.348
"This place is made
of pure love..."

45:41.281 --> 45:43.324
I told you I can't
sign anything for free,

45:43.491 --> 45:44.659
per my contract.

45:44.826 --> 45:45.827
[security guard]
Sorry, it's not that.

45:45.994 --> 45:47.370
Someone left something for you.

45:47.495 --> 45:49.289
-Who?
-That Make-A-Wish man

45:49.456 --> 45:51.416
from yesterday.
It's your script.

45:53.751 --> 45:56.546
He said tell you thanks
for making his wish come true.

46:13.062 --> 46:15.023
[door closes]

46:15.190 --> 46:17.984
[anticipatory music plays]

46:18.151 --> 46:19.611
♪ ♪

46:19.777 --> 46:22.363
[Bobby]
He's walking to his car.

46:22.530 --> 46:25.700
Hmm. It looks like
he's sending a text.

46:25.867 --> 46:27.702
-Or he's maybe writing notes.
-[Debbie] Notes are good,

46:27.827 --> 46:29.787
-Phone call would be better.
-Phone call is not better.

46:29.954 --> 46:31.331
He could be calling his barber.

46:31.498 --> 46:32.874
Mm. His hair's pretty short.

46:33.041 --> 46:34.459
Fine, his dentist.
His mother.

46:34.584 --> 46:36.211
We should all call
our moms more often.

46:36.377 --> 46:39.464
-Every day.
-Mine's dead. But I agree.

46:40.965 --> 46:42.258
[Jack] Okay, team.

46:49.224 --> 46:51.309
It's nothing yet.

46:52.435 --> 46:54.854
But it's not not nothing.

46:54.979 --> 46:57.815
Brooks Rizzo is clearly
looking to be impressed.

46:57.982 --> 47:00.902
And we have the opportunity
to impress him by showing him

47:01.027 --> 47:04.614
that what we do here
is special and unique

47:04.781 --> 47:06.741
and groundbreaking and
revolutionary and perfect

47:06.908 --> 47:09.911
for what he needs--
whatever that may be.

47:10.036 --> 47:11.955
Because
to tell y'all the truth,

47:12.080 --> 47:14.123
I don't really know
what all this involves.

47:14.290 --> 47:16.876
But I do know that
we got to reach up.

47:17.043 --> 47:18.670
We got to take it.

47:18.836 --> 47:22.090
We have to work harder than we
ever worked before, all of us.

47:22.257 --> 47:23.341
We need to take
this promotion.

47:23.508 --> 47:25.051
We need to turn it into

47:25.176 --> 47:28.429
what it always should have
been all along--opportunity.

47:28.596 --> 47:29.889
That's a rare thing.

47:30.056 --> 47:32.767
And I don't want to
look back and think

47:32.934 --> 47:35.436
this was our one chance
and we just let it slip away.

47:35.603 --> 47:38.314
I believe in all of you.

47:38.439 --> 47:41.109
You've always believed in me.

47:41.276 --> 47:43.611
So let's say
we do this together.

47:45.905 --> 47:47.365
[Wild Bill] D-W-L!

47:47.532 --> 47:50.785
[all] D-W-L! D-W-L!

47:50.952 --> 47:54.622
D-W-L! D-W-L!

47:54.789 --> 47:59.752
[chanting grows muffled,
echoes]

47:59.919 --> 48:02.797
[muffled]
D-W-L! D-W-L!

48:02.964 --> 48:09.512
[chanting continues, muffled]

48:09.679 --> 48:12.807
[soft, emotional music]

48:12.974 --> 48:15.143
-[click]
-[director] And action.

48:15.268 --> 48:18.646
[man] Sally said she's not
coming back to me.

48:18.813 --> 48:21.691
She's in love with
a World War II veteran.

48:21.816 --> 48:24.902
-What do I do?
-What do you do?

48:25.069 --> 48:27.196
You're in heaven, Sam!

48:27.363 --> 48:29.449
Surrounded by beauty.

48:29.616 --> 48:32.827
Maybe you just need
to open your eyes and realize

48:32.994 --> 48:35.330
the reason they call
them soulmates

48:35.455 --> 48:38.499
is 'cause you're not supposed
to meet 'em down there.

48:38.666 --> 48:42.295
You're supposed to
meet 'em up here.

48:44.130 --> 48:45.506
[director] And cut!
We got it.

48:45.673 --> 48:48.343
-[bell rings]
-Great work. Let's move on.

48:48.468 --> 48:50.970
Uh, can I get one more,
actually?

48:52.347 --> 48:54.015
Sorry, Bill, we gotta go.

48:54.182 --> 48:57.477
One more take.
For me, please.

48:58.978 --> 49:02.482
Okay.
Let's go again, one more time.

49:02.649 --> 49:04.609
Settle please.

49:04.776 --> 49:07.111
-[crewperson 1] Roll sound.
-[crewperson 2] Sound speed.

49:07.278 --> 49:08.655
[crewperson 3]
Scene 13. Take nine.

49:08.821 --> 49:09.822
-Mark.
-[click]

49:11.658 --> 49:13.034
And action.

49:13.201 --> 49:15.745
Sally said she's not
coming back to me.

49:15.912 --> 49:17.622
What do I do, Jerahmeel?

49:19.374 --> 49:22.210
This place,
it's made of pure love.

49:22.377 --> 49:26.339
But if you love something,
you can hurt it.

49:26.464 --> 49:29.217
And it can hurt you.
Purely.

49:29.384 --> 49:31.886
Not sure God
accounted for that.

49:34.055 --> 49:36.974
I fell for a girl
up here once,

49:37.141 --> 49:40.853
knew it the moment
she walked through that gate.

49:40.978 --> 49:45.066
She'd died young,
and we had a while together.

49:46.693 --> 49:49.070
And then one day,

49:49.237 --> 49:51.823
a man she'd loved down there
showed up.

49:53.700 --> 49:56.577
And when he walked in,

49:56.744 --> 50:00.456
she looked at him
the way I looked at her.

50:04.127 --> 50:07.380
That was a long time ago.

50:07.547 --> 50:10.049
Forever ago maybe.

50:11.217 --> 50:13.428
I don't know what
I'm saying, just that, uh...

50:13.594 --> 50:18.599
just 'cause this is heaven

50:18.766 --> 50:20.977
don't mean it can't be hell.

50:22.311 --> 50:24.480
-[director] Cut.
-[bell rings]

50:24.647 --> 50:27.024
-Shit, man.
-[director] That was...

50:29.110 --> 50:30.778
Damn.

50:30.945 --> 50:32.905
Thanks.

50:41.914 --> 50:44.041
[phone chimes]

50:48.421 --> 50:49.672
Carol.

50:49.839 --> 50:52.175
Long time no talk, missy.

50:52.300 --> 50:54.802
[Carol] Bill, I just thought
you should know,

50:54.969 --> 50:58.139
Tom shot himself this morning.

51:01.601 --> 51:02.894
What?

51:03.019 --> 51:05.480
Shot himself in the head.

51:08.065 --> 51:11.903
[uneven breathing]

51:12.069 --> 51:13.488
I just...I just...

51:13.654 --> 51:16.991
[Carol] He was too proud
to ask you for help.

51:17.158 --> 51:18.743
But you could've
helped him anyway.

51:18.910 --> 51:21.621
You could've done something,

51:21.788 --> 51:25.792
anything for him.

51:26.876 --> 51:28.503
You'll have to live
with that, I guess.

51:28.669 --> 51:32.840
[crying]
Yes.

51:33.007 --> 51:36.010
Yes, I will.

51:36.177 --> 51:38.638
Carol, are you okay?

51:38.805 --> 51:42.058
-You have a nice evening.
-[beep]

51:42.225 --> 51:45.061
[somber music]

51:45.228 --> 51:48.105
♪ ♪

51:49.857 --> 51:52.276
[sobs]

51:55.822 --> 51:57.198
[clears throat]
